<item>
            <title>[JCR-906] Introduce similarity function</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JCR-906</link>
                <project id="10591" key="JCR">Jackrabbit Content Repository</project>
                        <description>The query handler should support a similarity function that allows one to find nodes that are similar to a given existing one.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
Example:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
//*[rep:similar(&amp;quot;/foo/bar&amp;quot;)]&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
Finds nodes that are similar to node /foo/bar.</description>
                <environment></environment>
